Unknown.name: Appointment
Unknown.summary: Model for Appointments, usually lessons, but including other activities, that make up the schedule.
Unknown.remarks: To learn more about appointments, take a look at the official documentation over here.

properties.name: Base
properties.summary: True when this version is the first non-hidden one. JSON Key: base

properties.name: Branch
properties.summary: The branch of the school this appointment belongs to. JSON Key: branch

properties.name: BranchId
properties.summary: The id of the branch of the school this appointment belongs to. JSON Key: branchOfSchool

properties.name: Cancelled
properties.summary: True if the appointment is cancelled and no attendance is required. JSON Key: cancelled

properties.name: ChangeDescription
properties.summary: Textual description of the change. JSON Key: changeDescription

properties.name: Created
properties.summary: The date this version of the appointment was created. JSON Key: created

properties.name: End
properties.summary: The end time of the appointment (the first moment the appointment is no longer taking place). JSON Key: end

properties.name: EndTimeSlot
properties.summary: Timeslot during which the appointment ends. JSON Key: endTimeSlot

properties.name: Fields
properties.summary: A list of all JSON keys implemented in this model that can be returned by the API. This is the list that will be passed to the API by default in the related methods, unless stated otherwise.

properties.name: Groups
properties.summary: The groups of students participating in the appointment. JSON Key: groups

properties.name: Hidden
properties.summary: This appointment should not be shown to the user if this is true. An hidden appointment cannot be valid. JSON Key: hidden

properties.name: Id
properties.summary: The id of this version of the appointment. JSON Key: id

properties.name: InstanceId
properties.summary: The id of this instance of the appointment. Every instance has one or more versions. JSON Key: appointmentInstance

properties.name: LastModified
properties.summary: The date this version of the appointment was last modified. JSON Key: lastModified

properties.name: Locations
properties.summary: The locations (classrooms) where the appointment takes place. JSON Key: locations

properties.name: Modified
properties.summary: True if the appointment is modified. JSON Key: modified

properties.name: Moved
properties.summary: True if the time or location of the appointment is changed. JSON Key: moved

properties.name: New
properties.summary: True if the appointment was not originally scheduled. JSON Key: new

properties.name: Remark
properties.summary: A remark for the appointment. JSON Key: remark

properties.name: Start
properties.summary: The start time of the appointment. JSON Key: start

properties.name: StartTimeSlot
properties.summary: Timeslot during which the appointment starts. JSON Key: startTimeSlot

properties.name: Subjects
properties.summary: List of subjects. JSON Key: subjects

properties.name: Teachers
properties.summary: The teachers participating in the appointment. JSON Key: teachers

properties.name: Type
properties.summary: The type of appointment. JSON Key: type

properties.name: Valid
properties.summary: True if this appointment is part of the most up-to-date schedule. Only one version of an instance can be valid; a valid version can still be canceled. JSON Key: valid
